-MWC9i3CTQN29EGy84x3.text: The stolen vehicle is a white Buick with a Minneapolis license plate that read 491 PGG.

-MWCA03B3VjIzBVInx1Q.text: The suspects are said to be driving the car that was last seen heading westbound on Charles street.

-MWCARMJaqJ39Bq-b_5n.text: Police advice that the victim was also assaulted.
